               <p>The Prosecutor depos'd, That she going to move into the Country, employ'd the prisoner as a <rs id="t17270517-26-deflabel143" type="occupation">Porter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17270517-26-defend165 t17270517-26-deflabel143"></join>, to carry some of her Goods, and missing several Things, she made strict Enquiry after them, and found the Goods mentioned in the Indictment on the prisoner.</p>
