             depos'd; That he saw the prisoner in a Barge with the Bottle of Brandy, and asked how he came by it; upon which the prisoner endeavoured to get away, but this Deponent seized him on suspicion, and he then confes'd he stole it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17270517-26-person170">
